title: 08/10 Fantasy Football Podcast: Tight Ends Preview
description:
Rob Gronkowski/Travis Kelce early or Hunter Henry/Jack Doyle late? Or do we prefer the mid-round guys like Jordan Reed and Tyler Eifert? We've got everything you need to know about the TE position in 2017 ... How many TEs are we comfortable with as our starter (1:30)? Should you ever draft two TEs (12:30)? Sleepers, breakouts and busts (18:12) ... Complete ADP review (30:30) as we touch on Eifert's upside, Kyle Rudolph's targets, rookie TEs and late-round picks ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
